# The pipeline needs NO API keys — analysis runs in your Claude Code session via
# the /research-scan and /add-resource skills, and Twitter/article fetching uses
# Agent Reach (no paid API). Twitter auth (cookies) is stored by Agent Reach in
# ~/.agent-reach/config.yaml, NOT here.
#
# This file exists only to document that there are no required secrets. Copy to
# .env only if you add optional integrations later.

# Optional: override the Jina Reader endpoint (default https://r.jina.ai/)
# JINA_READER_URL=
